<br>
&quot;Oh Isis, Goddess of Truth, Of Life, grant thy daughter's prayer.  Grant me with but a fragment of thy glorious power, a speck of sand on your infinite beach of wisdom and might, so I may help this sickened man.&quot;<br>
<br>
Ayaka knelt before an altar of Isis, carved beautifully in marble.  Balder laid before her, on a pallet covered by a sheet, shivering and trembling with cold even as his skin burned so hot.  His eyes were half lidded, and dim.<br>
<br>
A light surrounded Ayaka and Balder, concentrating from the elfmaid's hands.  Her eyes glowing, she bent over his body and placed one hand over his feverish forehead and lackluster eyes, and another on his chest.  The power of her goddess surged through her, filling her with holy ecstacy.  And when the light faded, Balder lay still, his skin cool to the touch and his color returning.  No longer did he tremble, no longer did he gasp for air.  He slept the sleep of righteousness, of the innocent.<br>
<br>
Ayaka gave a weary smile.  <br>
<br>
She grasped the medallion on her neck, the one of moonstone.  &quot;Thank you, Isis,&quot; she breathed. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#060C65><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bcollisionworld.showUserPublicProfile?gid=spark@collisionworld>Spark</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.cheatingdome.com/forums/attachment.php?s=&postid=65686" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 231<br> <font color=#F5F5DC>(3/11/03 11:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fcollisionworldfrm158.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> eeeee!</span><hr size=1> &quot;Kirin quickly finished dressing and Eevee hollered at the elf man through the door again.<br>
